{"tid":426151,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"教大家刷積分拎馬會優越卡唔洗再排隊","createTime":"2017-10-06T11:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T06:35:38.000Z","uid":9504,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7df2898adf77b480a26be2fcdacf936dca0f33","tid":426151,"uid":9504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:03:35.000Z","msg":"方法好簡單<br />\n首先你入$200落馬會戶口 然後每星期等英超買英超強隊之一阿仙奴既盤或者讓球勝 再等兩個鐘 完場馬會會派彩比你 到時就有一個double 每星期都係咁 <br />\n200變400<br />\n400變800<br />\n800變1600<br />\n1600變3200<br />\n.........<br />\n最後完季 到時阿仙奴全勝姿態拎英超<br />\n你個戶口都累積唔少錢<br />\n馬會計晒你派彩金額 下年就可以拎張優越卡比你買六合彩唔洗再排隊<br />\n<br />\n上年我就係咁長追阿仙奴贏刷積分 絕無吹水<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/190304_33b369f2cbec98a6ae845504cdad9c60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F190304_33b369f2cbec98a6ae845504cdad9c60.jpg&h=72254f78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望大家支持阿仙奴！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5ae4e9bbd0f96a1f3f76f7352703e9cf0e2aec7f","tid":426151,"uid":9504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/190450_d96aa8eea842e60296c923e534651432.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F190450_d96aa8eea842e60296c923e534651432.jpg&h=e4bf229b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94ba7a31be47cf792b2e0d9e336b169af3d1a1eb","tid":426151,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"玩咁多年都未轉我做呢個<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"f851cfe8ab058c6041802f6585285006f9c7276d","tid":426151,"uid":26446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T11:05:17.000Z","msg":"Ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\